    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "为了阻止熔岩巨兽复活，\\n必须再次打倒复活的阿克欧王。\\n对此于心不忍的佩雷却犹豫不决。\\n最终，佩雷被赛丽艾拉和王子的话点醒，\\n为真正地尽忠，决意直面曾经的王！"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "喂！\\n快躲起来！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "是、是王！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110255_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛丽艾拉",
            "context": "怎么可能！我们不是打倒他了吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "你们看。\\n阿克欧王的身体……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "那是黑暗魔力吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "看来是黑暗魔力的影响\\n让阿克欧王复活了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "只要黑暗魔力继续从裂缝流入这里，\\n他就会不停地复活吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110255_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛丽艾拉",
            "context": "啧！真麻烦。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "不，这是不幸中的万幸。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "只要我们打倒阿克欧王，\\n就能获得异界碎片。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "对啊！\\n那我们快打倒阿克欧王吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "请等一下！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "怎么了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "熔岩巨兽可是不死之身。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "难道要一次次地前往异界，\\n一次次地击退熔岩巨兽吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "喂，你怎么了？\\n也太悲观了吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "是呀！不管能不能做到，\\n都应该先采取行动！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "那是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "你不是发誓\\n要阻止熔岩巨兽复活吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是因为不忍心讨伐王\\n才犹豫不决？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "我以为自己已经……\\n做好了拯救世界的觉悟。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "然而刚才王临终前的哀嚎，\\n仍在我耳边回响。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "而且，既然我无法拯救王的心智，\\n又有资格对他动武吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "还是说，即使世界毁灭\\n也要追随王才算是忠义吗……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "诶诶诶！眼睁睁地看着世界毁灭，\\n怎么想都很奇怪啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "但是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110255_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛丽艾拉",
            "context": "你只是因为自己觉得痛苦\\n而逃避现实罢了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110255_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛丽艾拉",
            "context": "这根本就不是\\n为对方着想。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "赛丽艾拉……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110255_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛丽艾拉",
            "context": "我也曾选择逃避，\\n不愿面对逃走的训练生们。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110255_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛丽艾拉",
            "context": "但是，尤蒂尔告诉我\\n“要相信自己付出的感情”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110255_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛丽艾拉",
            "context": "所以我决定面对现实。\\n因为我是真心为训练生们着想。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110255_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛丽艾拉",
            "context": "佩雷，你呢？\\n你对王的感情难道是假的吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "嗯？喂，快看！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120065_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "独眼食人王",
            "context": "嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "他想扩大裂缝？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "要是那样的话，\\n会有更多黑暗魔力流出！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "休想！\\n看招！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "慢着！\\n轻举妄动的话……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120065_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "独眼食人王",
            "context": "咕嗷嗷……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "被发现了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "怕什么。\\n本来就打算与之一战。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "而且要是让裂缝继续扩大，\\n会非常不妙！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110255_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛丽艾拉",
            "context": "上吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110255_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "3人",
            "context": "呀啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "我……我的感情……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不想战斗的话不用勉强。\\n阿克欧王由我们来对付。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "但我觉得谏诤犯错的王\\n也是你身为从者的使命。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我们上！\\n哈啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120065_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "独眼食人王",
            "context": "咕嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "我非常钦佩王……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110255_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "3人",
            "context": "呀啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120065_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "独眼食人王",
            "context": "咕嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "从前的王既贤明又高洁，\\n总是露出温柔的微笑。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "这家伙，比之前更强了吧！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "就算这样我们也不能输！\\n哈啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120065_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "独眼食人王",
            "context": "嘎啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "哇啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "尤蒂尔！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120065_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "独眼食人王",
            "context": "哈哈哈哈哈！\\n哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "从前的王……\\n不会以伤害他人为乐！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "阿克欧王！\\n现在的你被黑暗吞噬了心智！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "烈焰之柱！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120065_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "独眼食人王",
            "context": "唔嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "佩雷！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0069",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "异界空间的裂缝……\\n会随着时间自然修复。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "只要能在那段时间里，把熔岩巨兽\\n阻挡在异界空间就能解决这个问题。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "但是为了能长时间在异界活动，\\n需要大量的异界碎片。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "所以……一同打倒王，\\n收集异界碎片吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "你想通了啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_06_0074",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "多亏你让我清醒了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "这样下去的话，阿克欧之名\\n将作为昏君流传后世。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
